--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.4.0 (2020-11-25)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (httpd_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 2.3.2 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 2.3.1 (2020-05-05)
E: Minor cosmetic change

* Version 2.3.0 (2020-05-05)
F: Add option to define log_format combined (httpd_log_format_combined)
F: Add option to define log_format combinedio (httpd_log_format_combined_io)
F: Add option to define log_format combinedssl (httpd_log_format_combined_ssl)
F: Add option to define log_format common (httpd_log_format_common)

* Version 2.2.2 (2020-04-20)
E: Enable TLS version 1.3 by default

* Version 2.2.1 (2019-11-08)
B: Fix 'config' template location

* Version 2.2.0 (2019-10-13)
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 2.1.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 2.0.0 (2019-02-10)
C: Redesign 'httpd_config' option (alter config variable to string)
C: Redesign 'httpd_global_config' option (alter config variable to string)

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-13)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement
E: Rename config parameters

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-04-16)
F: Initial release
